            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut 2 A3 size sheets of<strong> non-stick baking paper</strong></p><p>Put the <strong>beef mixture</strong> between the two sheets and using a <strong>rolling pin</strong>, roll it out until approx. the thickness of a pound coin</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4 or more? You may need to do this in 2 batches!</p><p>Peel off the top baking sheet and transfer the <strong>rolled beef</strong> to a large baking tray (or two!) then add the tray[s] to the oven for 18-20 min or until cooked through and browned (no pink meat!)</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1664895111220-x200.jpg",
