      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice <strong>half</strong> your<strong> tomatoes<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>thinly, then chop the<strong> remaining</strong> <strong>tomato[es] </strong>roughly</p><p>Slice your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>finely</p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Remove 1<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>outer leaf per person from the <strong>lettuce</strong> and set aside, shred the <strong>inner core[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1664895114443-x200.jpg",
