            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your<strong> halloumi</strong> into chips</p><p>Add the <strong>remaining ground smoked paprika</strong> to a plate with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp] </span><strong>flour</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> halloumi chips </strong>to the plate and turn several times until fully coated in the flour mix</p><p>Combine your <strong>roasted garlic paste</strong>,<strong> natural yoghurt </strong>and <strong>chopped coriander </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>garlic sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1664895117195-x200.jpg",
