            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the beef is nearly ready, slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>brioche halves</strong> to a baking tray, cut side up, and put the tray in the oven for 4-5 min or until warmed through</p><p>Once the beef has browned, remove from the oven and pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Slice the <strong>browned</strong> <strong>beef</strong> into long strips – this is your<strong> beef doner meat</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
