          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1664895146886-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-copy-1664895146886-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fill the<strong> brioche bun </strong>with <strong>beef</strong> <strong>doner meat</strong>, a <strong>gem leaf</strong>, <strong>sliced tomato</strong>, some <strong>quick-pickled onion </strong>and <strong>garlic sauce</strong> – this is your <strong>beef doner kebab burger</strong></p><p>Top the<strong> halloumi fries </strong>with the<strong> mustard ketchup</strong>, <strong>sliced chilli </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), the <strong>remaining garlic sauce </strong>and<strong> quick-pickled onion</strong> – these are your <strong>loaded halloumi fries</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> with the <strong>chopped tomato</strong> and drizzle over the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>pickling liquid </strong>and enjoy!</p>",
